##Death and robbing the "air cut team" : A little careless is fatal threat

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Reporter, Zhu Xuan, correspondent, Du Weiwei, Zou Yaqin

"when the knife is removed, the airflow in the chest will eject with the new coronavirus. The surgeon first incises the lower edge of the thyroid cartilage to expose the trachea, then cuts the front wall of the Trachea, rapidly inserts the tracheal Cannula, inserts and fixes the silicone tube from the Cannula, and plugs in the suction machine..."the precise procedure takes 15 minutes to complete. "65,80,97, " the arterial Oxygenation on the bedside monitor shot up, and the patient's vital signs stabilized.

This is the scene when doctors in the East Hospital of Wuhan University People's Hospital Perform tracheotomy on a critically ill patient with new coronary pneumonia.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
"air-cut team" in the East Hospital of Wuhan University People's Hospital is performing tracheotomy for patients source: East Hospital of Wuhan University People's Hospital

The paper reported from the Eastern Hospital of Wuhan University People's Hospital on www.thepaper.cn  that on the afternoon of February 28, during a "human-snatching" battle with death, the three-member "qi-cutting team" led by Zhu Ting, director of the hospital's Otolaryngology, has won another victory. As of February 28, the team had completed 5 tracheotomies in critically ill patients with NCP.

It is reported that for the new coronary intubation critically ill patients, if 7-10 days can not be extubated, we need to do tracheotomy. During surgery, a large amount of the secretion of Aerosol will be ejected, the patient's lungs will be deposited in the virus particles directly exposed to the air. One false move, and it could be fatal to a paramedic.

Before each operation, members of the "air-cutting team" have to do a three-level protection, two layers of protective clothing, N95 masks, goggles, leg coverings... unlike other colleagues, they also have to wear positive pressure head coverings, four layers of gloves at the same time.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Tracheotomy on the surgeon's visual and tactile requirements are very high. Steam from the hood can block the surgeon's view, and four layers of gloves on both hands make it almost impossible for the knife's fingers to feel anything. In the visual and tactile "failure" of the case, each operation, Zhu Ting and teammates almost all rely on experience to complete.

On February 20, the OTOLARYNGOLOGY received an emergency call from the critical care unit. A 70 year old critically ill patient with Oxygenation pneumonia needed a tracheotomy after tracheal intubation, only 60% of the patients required a tracheotomy. "A tracheotomy must be performed as soon as possible, or the patient will soon die from respiratory failure, " said Zhou Chenliang, chief of critical care medicine, after a discussion with Kang Yan, chief of critical care medicine at Hwaseo hospital, decided to ask the "air cutting team" operating tracheotomy.

Zhu Ting with "gas cut small team" members Ding Yongjun, Deng Zhifeng changed protective clothing, the first time with gas cut bag rushed to the intensive care unit, and in the ward support of the Xinjiang medical team team team leader Yang Jianzhong to the stage. Postures, drapes, assessment, anesthesia, tracheotomy... After a series of precision percutaneous tracheostomy procedures and reattachment to a breathing machine, the patient's airway risk is reduced and comfort is immediately improved. And all the members of the chi-chih squad were drenched in sweat.

Zhu Ting said that the tracheotomy has a good auxiliary treatment effect in rescuing critically ill patients with new coronary pneumonia. "To reduce the mortality rate of patients with severe new pneumonia requires multi-disciplinary collaboration, and party members and doctors should lead the charge. As long as patients have needs, our 'qi-cutting team' will surely achieve its mission! "
